data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 5BR 3.5BA single family home in desirable Blooms Crossing neighborhood! Situated on a corner lot with 2 side load garage and spacious driveway. Enter into the bright 2 story foyer and continue into the spacious living and dining rooms with crown moldings. Updated kitchen with white cabinets, granite counters, hardwood floors and stainless steel appliances. The wood floors continue into the family room with recessed lights and gas fireplace.  The upper level has a primary bedroom suite with hardwood floors, crown molding, primary bath with new tile flooring and toilet, separate shower and soaking tub, double vanities and walk in closet. The upper level is host to the washer and dryer which is so convenient! The full finished basement is complete with a recreation room, den, 5th bedroom (currently used as a home gym) and 3rd full bathroom.  There's also a bonus room finished as a small office or use as extra storage, craft room, the ideas are endless! Other updates include upgraded powder room and hall bathroom, new basement floors, newer upper level carpet, roof 2018, washer 2019, dryer 2023.
